1
00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:02,290
Hey.

2
00:00:02,330 --> 00:00:03,880
That tie...

3
00:00:04,550 --> 00:00:06,880
Is it crooked?

4
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:08,970
It's too flashy for a rookie.

5
00:00:09,470 --> 00:00:10,470
Huh?

6
00:00:11,010 --> 00:00:12,140
I'm sorry.

7
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:15,020
I'll take it off right away.

8
00:00:16,850 --> 00:00:19,140
You can't meet clients looking like that.

9
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:21,270
Use mine for today.

10
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:32,320
Fix your tie and let's get to work.

11
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:35,740
Yes, sir.

12
00:00:40,620 --> 00:00:42,140
Okay.

13
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,890
I'm home.

14
00:00:56,890 --> 00:00:57,850
Welcome back.

15
00:00:58,980 --> 00:01:01,560
You're so late on your first day.

16
00:01:05,320 --> 00:01:07,610
Man, I'm exhausted.

17
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,780
How was work today?

18
00:01:12,820 --> 00:01:15,870
I want to quit.
